{{Top|leg}}
'''Shantee Ree''' was a famous [[Holovid/Legends|holovid]] star. She was perhaps best known for her "Save the Stohl" campaign. Ree owned a specially-trained [[Stohl|attack stohl]] named [[Needla]], which bit an overzealous fan during an autograph session. The media portrayed the attack as an assault. Shantee responded that the attack stohl had been trained to protect her. The result of the media coverage was that attack stohls were hunted for the fun of it, until Shantee Ree launched her campaign to save the species.<ref name="Creatures of the Galaxy">''[[Creatures of the Galaxy]]''</ref>

